==German==
===Etymology===
Possibly from common Germanic ''*jai'', from Proto-Indo-European ''*yāi'', extended from a pronominal root ''*i-''; near cognates including English [[yea]] and Gothic [[𐌾𐌰𐌹]] "truly".  

===Adverb===
'''je'''

# [[ever]]

====Related expressions====
*[[je länger je lieber]]
*[[je nachdem]]

